<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.4.6">
<l>piḷḷai kaḷceyvaṉa ceyyāy pēciṉpe ritum valiyai</l>
<l>kaḷḷam maṉattilu ṭaiyai kāṇavē tīmai kaḷceyti</l>
<l>yuḷḷa murukiyeṉ koṅkai yōṭṭantu pāynti ṭukiṉṟa</l>
<l>paḷḷik kuṟippu<supplied>c</supplied>cey  yātē pālamu tuṇṇanī vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You do not do what children do; if [your] strength is told, it is immense.</l>
<l>You have slyness in your heart; you do mischief [for all] to see.</l>
<l>[When my] heart melts, my breasts flow freely, creating a flood.</l>
<l>Without making a pretense of sleep, come to suckle my ambrosial milk.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
